"Add 1 extra workout or extend long session to shift toward Peaking." = "Agrega 1 entrenamiento extra o extiende la sesión larga para avanzar hacia Pico.";
"Begin ramping up training. Your body is ready for more stimulus." = "Empieza a aumentar el entrenamiento. Tu cuerpo está listo para más estímulo.";
"Below average. Start with consistent low-intensity cardio 4× per week. VO₂ max responds well to training — early gains are large." = "Debajo del promedio. Empieza con cardio consistente de baja intensidad 4× por semana. El VO₂ máx responde bien al entrenamiento — las ganancias iniciales son grandes.";
"Elite-level aerobic capacity. Your VO₂ max is in the top tier — associated with exceptional longevity and cardiovascular protection." = "Capacidad aeróbica de nivel élite. Tu VO₂ máx está en el nivel más alto — asociado con longevidad excepcional y protección cardiovascular.";
"High stress without enough recovery. If sustained, leads to overtraining. Prioritize sleep, reduce intensity, and add rest days." = "Alto estrés sin suficiente recuperación. Si se mantiene, lleva al sobreentrenamiento. Prioriza el sueño, reduce la intensidad y agrega días de descanso.";
"Low aerobic capacity. Even modest increases in walking or easy cycling produce significant VO₂ max gains. Start gradually." = "Baja capacidad aeróbica. Incluso aumentos modestos en caminata o ciclismo fácil producen ganancias significativas de VO₂ máx. Empieza gradualmente.";
"Low training load with high recovery capacity. Perfect for taper weeks before a race, or deload blocks." = "Baja carga de entrenamiento con alta capacidad de recuperación. Perfecto para semanas de descarga antes de una carrera.";
"Moderate aerobic fitness. Regular Zone 2 cardio (150+ min/week) will meaningfully improve VO₂ max within 8–12 weeks." = "Fitness aeróbico moderado. Cardio regular en Zona 2 (150+ min/semana) mejorará significativamente el VO₂ máx en 8–12 semanas.";
"Moderate stress and recovery — sustainable long-term training. Gradually increase stimulus to enter the Peaking quadrant." = "Estrés y recuperación moderados — entrenamiento sostenible a largo plazo. Aumenta gradualmente el estímulo para entrar al cuadrante de Pico.";
"Optimal zone: you’re absorbing training well. Your body is recovering faster than the stress. This is where fitness gains happen." = "Optimal zone: you’re absorbing training well. Your body is recovering faster than the stress. This is where fitness gains happen.";
"Outstanding aerobic fitness. Sustaining this through consistent Zone 2 training and periodic hard efforts will maintain your advantage." = "Fitness aeróbico excepcional. Mantenerlo con entrenamiento constante en Zona 2 y esfuerzos intensos periódicos conservará tu ventaja.";
"Reduce volume 20–30%. Add a rest day. Prioritize 8h+ sleep." = "Reduce el volumen 20–30%. Agrega un día de descanso. Prioriza 8h+ de sueño.";
"Solid foundation. Structured endurance training — 3–4 aerobic sessions/week with one tempo workout — will move you to ‘Good’." = "Solid foundation. Structured endurance training — 3–4 aerobic sessions/week with one tempo workout — will move you to ‘Good’.";
"Stay the course. Maintain load and protect recovery habits." = "Mantén el rumbo. Conserva la carga y protege tus hábitos de recuperación.";

